---
title: Stokes Burger with Rustic Chips and Rocket Salad (F)
description: Fred Astaire and Ginger Rogers, Batman and Robin, Luke and Bianca*. There are some things that simply go better together. That’s why we knocked up this ludicrously luscious burger with our favourite BBQ sauce from Stokes. A little injection of summer into the winter cold!

*Our latest Fresh Farm romance. Awww.
